 

Basic Building Blocks

1)Module - To import 3rd party modules (root module) 2) Component -To create html, css and ts file



Bacis Commands


1)ng new project_name - To create a new project

2)ng gc Component_name To create a new component 

3)ng serve --open To run Angular file

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1)Data Binding

share data between components

ts ---> component 
html---> view

   a)One way data binding(1 direction)
    ts -> html or html -> ts

      a.1) Component to view 

         i)String  interpolation (1 direction ) - {{expression}}
         ii) Property Binding - [attribute name]="property"
    a.2) View to component
        
        i) Event binding (1 direction) - (event_name)="function_name()";
        ii) Event binding usin $ event (event_name)="function_name($event)";
